Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 13/8/2024

1. Introduction

Welcome to the Mchezo App. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our application. By using the Mchezo App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

2. Information We Collect

Personal Information: When you register and join a group, we collect personal details such as your name, phone number, and email address.
Transaction Information: We collect data related to your deposits, withdrawals, and group activities.
Usage Data: We collect information on how you interact with the app, including IP addresses, browser types, and usage patterns.
3. How We Use Your Information

To Provide and Maintain the Service: Manage your account, process transactions, and enhance app functionality.
To Communicate with You: Send notifications about updates, changes, and offers related to the app.
For Security: Monitor for fraudulent activities and ensure the safety of our users.
To Analyze Usage: Understand app usage patterns to improve user experience.
4. How We Share Your Information

With Administrators: Admins may access certain information for managing groups and transactions.
With Service Providers: We may share information with third-party services that assist in operating the app.
For Legal Requirements: We may disclose information if required by law or to protect our rights.
5. Data Security

We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.

6. Your Rights

Access and Update: You can access and update your personal information through the app.
Delete Account: You may request to delete your account and personal information at any time.
7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.

8. Contact Us

For any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at gkyando5@gmail.com.
